23/12/2005
SKOPJE, Macedonia -- Prime Minister Vlado Buckovski received a letter from US President George W. 
Bush on Thursday (22 December), congratulating Macedonia for its success in achieving EU candidate status. 
The two leaders met in Washington in October.
In a speech to parliament Thursday, President Branko Crvenkovski said candidate status is an historic opportunity that should not be missed. 
(MIA, Makfax, A1 TV - 22/12/05)
